attributes.title: WEARING A DEAD MAN'S HAT • MADDEN NFL 19
attributes.description: Things are gettin' super spicy in Mathis! Lo tries to raise money on the internet the only way she knows how, while Colt struts around in his dead coach's hat.

attributes.title: PANIC AT THE PIER • POKEMON LET'S GO PIKACHU CHALLENGE
attributes.description: In beautiful Southern California, even the winters are warm enough for a nice trip to the beach.  And that seems like the perfect place to find some Pokemon.  Luckily, everyone at the pier was super helpful and friendly and wanted nothing but to help James, Aleks, and Alec catch some of their favorite Pokemon.

attributes.title: DEATH BRINGS THE PAIN • POKEMON LET'S GO PIKACHU CHALLENGE
attributes.description: After meeting their social requirement of being outside for an hour, the boys retreat back to the safety of the warehouse for more Pokemon action.  But when death comes knocking at the door, they realize that they were actually safer outside.

attributes.title: RUBBIN THE SEAMAN • POKEMON LET'S GO PIKACHU CHALLENGE
attributes.description: Aleks' balls have finally seemed to recover just in time to play with more seamen.  All aboard on yet another battle filled episode on the S.S. Get Your Pokemon Killed Here.  Who knows what will happen.

attributes.title: THE FINALE • MADDEN NFL 19
attributes.description: Longshot 2 comes to a close...FINALLY.

attributes.title: THE NEVER ENDING BATTLE • POKEMON LET'S GO PIKACHU CHALLENGE
attributes.description: This is it.  The final battle.  We only have a handful of Pokemon left, and are about to battle a gym that will surely kill us and finally put an end of this series.  One can only hope.

attributes.title: BROTHERHOOD OF THE TRAVELING ALS  • GEOGUESSR GAMEPLAY
attributes.description: Seasoned world travelers Aleks and Alec play GeoGuessr and prove that if they woke up in a different part of the world with no recollection of how they got there....they would die.

attributes.title: THE BIG BRO I NEVER HAD • PLAYSTATION CLASSIC
attributes.description: Watch as we take a trip down memory lane back to when we were just a couple of baby gamers.

attributes.title: BATTLE OF THE BEYBLADE BOYZ
attributes.description: Prepare yourself for the most epic Beyblade battle ever recorded after you've read the most sarcastic description that's ever been written.

attributes.title: DARK SOULS RANDOMIZED
attributes.description: You asked for it!!!!  We're delivering it!!!  We're back to playing video games!!!  In fact we're playing Dark Souls!!!  But why play Dark Souls a regular way when we can randomize it with mods!!!  How can that possibly go wrong!?!?!?

attributes.title: THE PACIFY NIGHTMARE
attributes.description: GAMEPLAY!!!  Holy crap we're playing a PC game!  I haven't seen those computers in years!!!  But after playing a game like Pacify, the nightmare fueled comedy starring Aleks and Alec, we might never see those computers again.  Oh well, best of luck fellas!

attributes.title: GETTING ADDICTED TO JAPANESE UFO CATCHERS
attributes.description: Who loves playing online games?!?  Club Penguin am I right?!?  Well too bad!!!  We're traveling all the way to Japan, via the internet, to blow more of our valuable money on worthless prizes and rigged crane games that are probably sitting in someones garage.  What will the great land of Japan bestow upon us for our mighty crane efforts???

attributes.title: SEGA THROWBACK
attributes.description: The Big Bro/Lil' Bro duo is back getting nostalgic with another classic console. This time, it's the Sega Genesis.

attributes.title: METRO EXODUS GAMEPLAY
attributes.description: Aleks helps guide Alec through the the post-apocalyptic ruins of his motherland in the new Metro Exodus.

attributes.title: THIS GAME WAS BANNED ON STEAM?
attributes.description: Today Aleks wants to show Lindsey a little game. A super fun nice easy going relaxing... creepy.... haunting game!

attributes.title: THE SCARIEST BANNED TAIWANESE GAME CONTINUED
attributes.description: Today Aleks wants to show Lindsey a little game. A super fun nice easy going relaxing... creepy.... haunting game!

attributes.title: THE FINALE OF THE BANNED HORROR GAME
attributes.description: Today Aleks wants to show Lindsey a little game. A super fun nice easy going relaxing... creepy.... haunting game! Let's check out what happens in the finale of this series.

attributes.title: ULTIMATE FIGHTING ARCADE MACHINE
attributes.description:
The Big Bro/Lil' Bro duo is back AGAIN and this time gettin' down on the throwback emulator with over 1500 games. 

Trigger Warning: They don't play all 1500 games.

attributes.title: SCUFFED RETRO NINTENDO
attributes.description: Big Bro & Lil' Bro check out some scuffed versions of classic Nintendo games

attributes.title: ATARI FLASHBACK CONSOLE
attributes.description: The brothers are back at again smashin' the joystick on the Atari retro console. It's just a paper weight with a USB drive in it.

attributes.title: BURNING OUR EYE SOCKETS - SEKIRO MODDED
attributes.description: HEY!!!  We're playing a game that's not more than 20 years old today!!!  But don't worry, we miss the 80's as much as you do so we decided to bring the 80's to Sekiro!!!!  I'm sure this is a great idea that won't burn anyone's eye sockets into neon hell!!!

attributes.title: THE "REAL" NES CONSOLE FROM THE 80's
attributes.description: After being scammed FOUR times, Aleks has finally gotten his hands on the actual retro NES console from the 1980's.

attributes.title: THE BLOOD BATH OF MORDHAU
attributes.description: WAIT A MINUTE!!!!  Are those gaming PCs that we are playing with???  That's right we dusted off the old gaming computers and decided to play a game again!  Of course since we brought these puppies out we had to play the most popular game out there, Mordhau!!!!  Why?  Because horses!!!

attributes.title: THE BLOOD BATH OF MORDHAU - Part 2
attributes.description: Who wants more PC Gaming?!?!  Everyone of course!!! Luckily we recorded two episodes of everyone's favorite game Mordhau!  More killing, more bloodshed, more horses!!!  Along with some casual team killing!  I'm sure this will go well.

attributes.title: WE'RE HORRIBLE HUNTERS
attributes.description: Last time we tried to play this game it didn't fair so hot, basically we got our asses handed to us.  Luckily we've been practicing and we even unintentionally enlisted the help of a famous Twitch streamer to help us win!!  We can't lose!!!!

attributes.title: IMMORTAL DEER HUNTING
attributes.description: Moving to LA has made us forget about our redneck roots.  Luckily The Hunter: Call of the Wild has brought our roots back to us with all the glory of killing deer with our friends.  Finally we have a chance to show you our real life skills simulated in a game.

attributes.title: THE WORST ATV RIDE EVER
attributes.description: We loved shooting animals in the butt so much we thought we would do it again.  But this time, we're after a bear.  We did so well with the deer I don't see how this could possibly go wrong.

attributes.title: 140 GEOGUESSR IQ
attributes.description: We've been all around the world, and it shows. Well traveled boys with giant IQ's just crushing some geography on the ol' google maps game, GeoGuessr.

attributes.title: MY FRIEND ALEKS • MY FRIEND PEDRO GAMEPLAY
attributes.description: Aleks and Alec have a chill time playing My Friend Pedro.

attributes.title: BIG BRO LIL' BRO RETROCADE
attributes.description: Brett & Aleks sit down once again to test out the waters on another retro emulator, and it's just a real chill time you guys.

attributes.title: JUMP SCARE SIMULATOR • MAN OF MEDAN PT 1
attributes.description:
The fellas sit down for a long, scary, relaxing, and confusing journey 
through Man of Medan.

attributes.title: THE PIRATES OF DIVERSITY • MAN OF MEDAN PT 2
attributes.description: The MOM saga continues with Garrett at the helm. Will he make all the wrong moves? Will Conrad bang Fliss? Will Aleks put his sunglasses on? Will they finally kill that fly? Are there any other questions I can ask to fill space?

attributes.title: DISTRIBUTOR, NO CAP (ft. Drake) • MAN OF MEDAN PT 3
attributes.description: MOM part three is here and Garrett is STILL playing.

attributes.title: TITANIC BUT WITH GHOSTS • MAN OF MEDAN PT 4
attributes.description: The MOM saga continues as the boys drink Red Bull and eat Chipotle. This video is not brought to you by Red Bull or Chipotle.

attributes.title: BOAT MURDER GHOST MYSTERY • MAN OF MEDAN FINALE
attributes.description: The MOM Finale couldn't have come sooner!!! Strap one on for this series ender that's sure to save the channel.
